com.ibm.team.workitem.common.model

Interface IAttribute

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IAttributeHandle, IAuditable, IAuditableHandle, IItem, IItemHandle, IManagedItem, IManagedItemHandle, IProjectScoped

    public interface IAttribute
extends IAttributeHandle, IAuditable, IProjectScoped
    An attribute of a work item. Both built-in and custom attributes of work items are represented as IAttributes in the repository. An IAttribute is scoped to a project area, carries meta-data like the data-type and can be used to access the values of work items in the same project area.
    Since:
    0.5
    See Also:
    IWorkItem.getValue(IAttribute), IWorkItem.getCustomAttributes(), IWorkItemCommon.findAttributes(IProjectAreaHandle, IProgressMonitor), IWorkItemCommon.createNewAttribute(IProjectAreaHandle, String, String, String, IProgressMonitor)
